# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-3/apush-the-american-revolution/a/pontiacs-uprising">http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-3/apush-the-american-revolution/a/pontiacs-uprising</a>.
