# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-3/apush-the-american-revolution/a/the-intolerable-acts-and-the-first-continental-congress">http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-3/apush-the-american-revolution/a/the-intolerable-acts-and-the-first-continental-congress</a>.
