# (format: perseus_text)
#: intl/datastore:1
msgid "**An 1856 map of the United states featuring free states (red), slave states (gray), US territory that has not yet become a state (green), and the territory in question, Kansas (white).** [Image](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kansas%E2%80%93Nebraska_Act#/media/File:Reynolds%27s_Political_Map_of_the_United_States_1856.jpg) courtesy of Wikimedia commons. "
msgstr ""

# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-5/apush-sectional-tension-1850s/a/the-kansas-nebraska-act">http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-5/apush-sectional-tension-1850s/a/the-kansas-nebraska-act</a>.
