msgstr ""

# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-7/apush-1920s-america/a/1920s-consumption">http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-7/apush-1920s-america/a/1920s-consumption</a>.
