msgstr ""

# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-7/apush-1920s-america/a/jazz-and-the-lost-generation">http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-7/apush-1920s-america/a/jazz-and-the-lost-generation</a>.
