# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-8/apush-1950s-america/a/atomic-fears-and-the-arms-race">http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-8/apush-1950s-america/a/atomic-fears-and-the-arms-race</a>.
