msgstr ""

# Article is at <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-8/apush-civil-rights-movement/a/african-american-veterans-and-the-civil-rights-movement">http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-8/apush-civil-rights-movement/a/african-american-veterans-and-the-civil-rights-movement</a>.
