# Title of tutorial article <a href="http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-8/apush-postwar-era/a/the-cold-war-part-1">http://translate.khanacademy.org/humanities/ap-us-history/period-8/apush-postwar-era/a/the-cold-war-part-1</a>
# (KA_SOURCE_TREE: de)
